{"tid":530313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大婆旺角斬二奶 高呼：做乜勾我老公","createTime":"2018-01-15T15:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T17:08:58.000Z","uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fab0afa37766fd08bc5aacb8699fdc329587c20f","tid":530313,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T15:38:41.000Z","msg":"旺角發生斬人案，晚上近9時，兩名女子於奶路臣街11號一幢大廈大堂內發生爭執，並大打出手，未幾更有人亮刀襲擊對方。警方到場拘捕涉嫌傷人女子，兩人均報稱受傷，分別送往廣華醫院及伊利沙伯醫院接受治理。其中一名涉嫌傷人女子接受治理後被警方拘捕，並帶返警署調查。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，被捕女子為大婆，她懷疑對方勾引其丈夫，糾纏期間一度高呼「做乜勾我老公」，之後便亮刀斬傷二奶。<br />\n大廈的大堂遺下大灘血迹，保安員周先生向記者表示，當時見兩名女子爭執糾纏，互相扯頭髮，其中一人怒斥對方「勾咗佢老公」，並取出利刀襲擊對方，周見狀上前勸止，但兩名女子未有理會，他於是報案。周先生稱，上址經常發生打交等事件，已見慣不怪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180115/57712153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180115%2F57712153&d=QO%2BpW4VwUfY1%2B8WOlimGx54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e645e177\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180115%2F57712153&h=0bebf11d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180115/57712153</a>"},{"pid":"fb96249fe36e95d2f2e0ed93854d4cfa66d0f092","tid":530313,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"ＦＹＲ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/530010/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/530010/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n搞人老公爛卵巢：『有圖』東 方為X妹妹 畸x 個樣係咪好淫"},{"pid":"51cff33bd5ba0f09d367c303db498cb38c4a6064","tid":530313,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T15:55:07.000Z","msg":"癲過大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c2b44f3ef01c5a9ad68aa1eb848d0a9b501030","tid":530313,"uid":833,"like":5,"dislike"